  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/4dcc3ba0978aa49cbfddbbd61837ebc1.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction/h2]<br><br>\"Xuan Nu Zhu Mo Lu\" is a traditional style 2D action adventure game. Players will fight with many demons in many scenes, meet and help the innocent, and finally uncover the truth of the ten thousand demons grottoes and Xuannv.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/175ebe7cb02a1a6b92d78db8639ab824.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=334 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br></h2><li>Detailed 2D hand-painted art<br><br>All the materials in this game are hand-drawn.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/819b62f2c898b0b644513455a5501f1b.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/34f9c3afac6a18269eaa765f3b7daee5.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/a21031b47922809e843e49c1ab30db73.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=282 /></span><br><br><br></li><li>Beautiful and lovely girl<br>The protagonist of the game is a young, beautiful and superb martial arts girl with more than 200 frames of full hand-painted animation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/c9f656a1e848702b7103c384c7f08484.poster.avif?t=1667183493\" width=560 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/c9f656a1e848702b7103c384c7f08484.webm?t=1667183493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/c9f656a1e848702b7103c384c7f08484.mp4?t=1667183493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br><br></li><li>Exquisite character drawing<br>There are many exquisite characters in the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/3b8027df9433dba1ccd4b221ef8d406c.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=380 /></span><br><br></li><li>Rich 2D action elements<br>In the game, players can operate the protagonist to move, jump, double jump, sprint, climb, hang, combo, use spirit power and many other actions, and can use various means to kill the enemy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/2927ddb4169637862f7a0df91cc722fa.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br></li><li>Exploring the interconnected world<br>Players' adventure will be explored in many huge and different styles of the world, such as deep temples, evil caves and so on!      <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/32c2bc4247e2d1fa8a96a1436783c60b.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=1542 /></span><br><br></li><li>Dozens of strange enemies with different styles<br>Many demons enemies and epic level demons! Face and kill the most evil demons in the adventure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490460/extras/4e703b2c99360e6f56c60fdb48824cf6.avif?t=1667183493\" width=600 height=608 /></span></li></ul>",
